      <hedline>
        <hl1>Cleaning the Kitchen Sponge</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''You Can Disinfect a Kitchen Sponge by Microwaving It'' (Really?, March 27): Your article was a real eye-opener, but the suggestion that we simply throw smelly sponges away is another instance of our all-too-wasteful attitude toward consumer goods. A neighbor offered a better alternative to me several years ago: run sponges through the dishwasher every few days. It really works; it would save landfill space, and money, too!</p>
        <p>Ellen C. Schwartz  Ann Arbor, Mich.</p>
      </block>
